metadata.name: Merge
metadata.description:
The art challenges the technology, and the technology inspires the art. Endless loop of inspiration is the driving force of human evolution.

Technology revolutionise our lives, but  art  and stories we tell frame our response. Advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic. 
It's still magic even if you know how it's done.




Ai + Digital Painting + Photoshop 

August 2022
